---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Legacy Window Tint | Phoenix Window Tinting Experts"
	description="Family-owned window tinting experts serving Phoenix and Maricopa County. Licensed, insured, and committed to quality. Trusted Arizona professionals."
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Legacy Window Tint</h1>
			<p class="hero-subtitle">Serving Phoenix Homeowners</p>
			<p class="hero-intro">We're local window tinting experts who understand Arizona heat. We've helped thousands of Phoenix homeowners cut energy bills, protect their homes, and stay comfortable year-round.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Why Choose Us -->
	<section class="why-choose">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Why Phoenix Homeowners Choose Us</h2>

			<div class="reasons-grid">
				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/>
							<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Trusted Local Experts</h3>
					<p>We've installed window film on thousands of Arizona homes. We know what works in our extreme climate and we stand behind every installation.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
							<polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Local Family Business</h3>
					<p>We're not a national chain. We live here, work here, and care about our neighbors. Your home matters to us because this is our community too.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/>
							<path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Licensed & Insured</h3>
					<p>Fully licensed, bonded, and insured for your protection. We carry comprehensive liability coverage and workers' compensation.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
							<path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Premium GeoShield Films</h3>
					<p>We only install superior quality GeoShield films - proven to perform in Arizona's extreme heat with industry-leading heat rejection.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
							<circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Expert Installation</h3>
					<p>Our installers are trained, certified professionals with years of experience. We prep properly, work clean, and get it right the first time.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="reason-card">
					<div class="reason-icon">
						<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Lifetime Warranty</h3>
					<p>Every installation includes a lifetime manufacturer warranty against peeling, bubbling, or discoloration. We're here for the long haul.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Service Area -->
	<section class="service-area">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Proudly Serving All of Maricopa County</h2>
			<p class="section-intro">From Sun City to Gilbert, we bring professional window tinting to homeowners across the Phoenix metro area.</p>

			<div class="cities-grid">
				<div class="city-group">
					<h3>North Phoenix</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Scottsdale</li>
						<li>Paradise Valley</li>
						<li>North Phoenix</li>
						<li>Cave Creek</li>
						<li>Carefree</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="city-group">
					<h3>West Valley</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Surprise</li>
						<li>Peoria</li>
						<li>Glendale</li>
						<li>Goodyear</li>
						<li>Buckeye</li>
						<li>Avondale</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="city-group">
					<h3>East Valley</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Mesa</li>
						<li>Tempe</li>
						<li>Chandler</li>
						<li>Gilbert</li>
						<li>Queen Creek</li>
						<li>Apache Junction</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="city-group">
					<h3>Central & South</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Phoenix</li>
						<li>Ahwatukee</li>
						<li>Laveen</li>
						<li>Tolleson</li>
						<li>Sun City</li>
						<li>Fountain Hills</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="service-note">Don't see your city? We serve the entire Phoenix metro area and surrounding communities. Give us a call!</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Our Values -->
	<section class="values">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Our Commitment to You</h2>

			<div class="values-grid">
				<div class="value-card">
					<h3>No Pressure, Ever</h3>
					<p>We hate pushy salespeople as much as you do. You'll get honest information, fair pricing, and zero pressure tactics. We earn your business with quality, not gimmicks.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="value-card">
					<h3>Transparent Pricing</h3>
					<p>No bait-and-switch. No hidden fees. We provide clear, detailed quotes up front so you know exactly what you're getting and what it costs.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="value-card">
					<h3>Quality Workmanship</h3>
					<p>We don't cut corners. From surface prep to final installation, we follow manufacturer specifications to ensure your film performs perfectly for decades.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="value-card">
					<h3>Customer Satisfaction</h3>
					<p>Your happiness is our success. We're not done until you're thrilled with your cooler, more comfortable home and the money you're saving every month.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA Section -->
	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="cta-box">
				<h2>Ready to Beat the Arizona Heat?</h2>
				<p>Join thousands of Phoenix homeowners who trust Legacy Window Tint for professional installation and real results.</p>

				<div class="cta-stats">
					<div class="cta-stat">
						<strong>$150-300</strong>
						<span>Average Monthly Savings</span>
					</div>
					<div class="cta-stat">
						<strong>3-4 Hours</strong>
						<span>Typical Installation Time</span>
					</div>
					<div class="cta-stat">
						<strong>Lifetime</strong>
						<span>Warranty Included</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="cta-group">
					<a href="tel:888-887-5897" class="btn btn-phone phone-large">
						<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
							<path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
						</svg>
						Call 888-887-5897
					</a>
					<a href="/#quote-form" class="btn btn-primary">Calculate My Price</a>
				</div>

				<p class="cta-fine-print">Free quotes. No obligation. Same-week installation available.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--gray-900) 100%);
		color: var(--white);
		padding: 80px 20px 60px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--gold);
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.hero-intro {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 60px 20px 40px;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}
	}

	/* Why Choose Us */
	.why-choose {
		padding: 80px 20px;
		background: var(--gray-50);
	}

	.why-choose h2 {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 50px;
	}

	.reasons-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 30px;
		max-width: 1100px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.reason-card {
		background: var(--white);
		padding: 35px 30px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.reason-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--gold);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
	}

	.reason-icon {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.reason-icon svg {
		stroke: var(--gold);
	}

	.reason-card h3 {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		color: var(--gray-900);
		font-size: 1.25rem;
	}

	.reason-card p {
		color: var(--gray-700);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
	}

	/* Service Area */
	.service-area {
		padding: 80px 20px;
		background: var(--white);
	}

	.service-area h2 {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.section-intro {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--gray-700);
		margin-bottom: 50px;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.cities-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 40px;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto 40px;
	}

	.city-group h3 {
		margin-bottom: 15px;
		color: var(--gray-900);
		border-bottom: 3px solid var(--gold);
		padding-bottom: 10px;
	}

	.city-group ul {
		list-style: none;
	}

	.city-group li {
		padding: 8px 0;
		color: var(--gray-700);
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 20px;
	}

	.city-group li:before {
		content: '→';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--gold);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.service-note {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--gray-700);
		font-style: italic;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* Values */
	.values {
		padding: 80px 20px;
		background: var(--gray-50);
	}

	.values h2 {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 50px;
	}

	.values-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 30px;
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.value-card {
		background: var(--white);
		padding: 35px 30px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.value-card h3 {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		color: var(--gray-900);
	}

	.value-card p {
		color: var(--gray-700);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
	}

	/* CTA Section */
	.cta-section {
		padding: 80px 20px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--gray-900) 100%);
	}

	.cta-box {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta-box h2 {
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}

	.cta-box > p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	.cta-stats {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 40px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	.cta-stat {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 5px;
	}

	.cta-stat strong {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--gold);
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.cta-stat span {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--gray-300);
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 15px;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}

	.phone-large {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		padding: 18px 36px;
	}

	.cta-fine-print {
		color: var(--gray-300);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	/* Mobile Responsiveness */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.cta-group {
			flex-direction: column;
			width: 100%;
		}

		.cta-stats {
			gap: 20px;
		}

		.phone-large {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.story,
		.why-choose,
		.service-area,
		.values,
		.cta-section {
			padding: 50px 20px;
		}

		.reasons-grid,
		.cities-grid,
		.values-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>

<script>
	// Smooth scroll for anchor links
	document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
		anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
			e.preventDefault();
			const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
			if (target) {
				target.scrollIntoView({
					behavior: 'smooth',
					block: 'start'
				});
			}
		});
	});
</script>
